message.content: cs.CY, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.LG, cs.ET - The paper discusses the creation and development of a cloud-based learning and research environment for universities, which involves the use of various computational and technological tools. This falls under the category of Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of open education and open science principles, which are relevant to the categories of Digital Libraries (cs.DL) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the specific principles inherent to cloud-based systems, which falls under the category of Emerging Technologies (cs.ET).
